---
description: Refactoring rule based on imported external guidance
alwaysApply: false
---

Use this rule only when explicitly refactoring existing code.

Rules:
- preserve external behavior
- make small reversible changes
- do not mix refactoring with new features
- keep tests passing between steps
- avoid broad rewrites
- explain what behavior was preserved
- stop when the code is clearer, not when it is perfect

Use the imported reference file when useful:

